“Here’s to the Beautiful Girls “ 💎🎀💕 | I have been dreaming of brining this act to the big stage for almost 2 years now and I am excited for finally share media of it from @teaseproductions 9 year anniversary show. I started constructing my Ziegfeld Follies  inspired Costume in April 2021 First with the dress and then the Corset, Bra, and Panty. I commissioned a glorious cape from @moniquecierralingerie and Hand embellished @louboutinworld.  I was so excited when I got word that the anniversary show was happening I knew exactly what act I wanted to do. I always thought having troupe of male kittens by my side in exchange for the females( Like in the original film) was a great way to make the act light and campy. Something much more on brand for me.  Producer, Creator , amd Choreographer of this increíble show @missdonnahood did an amazing job putting choreography together for the male kittens in less than a weeks rehearsal time before the big show date. I also want to thank the dancers for being such incredible performers and helping this come to life. I had a lot of requests and  unnecessary creative “ needs “ when it came to my vision for this act. Like wanting  a two Showgirl Fan Reveal ( fans made by @donna.touch ) , Giant Scratching post for my kitties and requesting the tightest dance pants possible for my male dancers😂🔥🍆. All of which Donna gladly entertained and made happen. I was up every night till about 3 am the week of the show putting hundreds rhinestones on the kitten masks , cause black leather just wasn’t sparkly enough for me , ( Swipe to see some of the process) and then made 4 pairs of matching black rhinestones gloves  with pink. Bracelets and matching  hot pink nails! Meow And finally I Created a new garter skirt belt and pasties to top it all off 💋💕 Sorry to write so much I just am so proud of how this all came together. 💕Too see a full recap and making of this show head over to @teaseproductions where they have a full video series on their page!
